snippet.title: Zoo-ika Trailer
snippet.description:
Hi! I made a little video game with my friend, Maya Kern!
You can play it free in your browser on desktop and mobile at: https://funwalker.itch.io/zoo-ika

Maya made all of the art. You can find her here: https://bio.site/mayakern
And I did all of the coding. See more of my stupid junk at: https://funwalker.itch.io

--------------------------------------------
Wow! Two videos in two years! What a windfall.
